      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Grid convergence index (GCI) computed per Roache methodology. Final mesh of 4.2M polyhedral cells yields GCI < 3.1% for relative hemolysis index, exceeding MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
